Package: r4subui
Title: Interactive Dashboard for Clinical Submission Readiness
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Pawan Rama", "Mali", , "prm@outlook.in", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides an interactive Shiny dashboard for the R4SUB ecosystem.
    Visualizes evidence tables, pillar scores, the Submission Confidence Index
    (SCI), risk registers, traceability coverage, and trend analysis. Supports
    upload of evidence data or direct integration with 'r4subcore', 'r4subtrace',
    'r4subrisk', and 'r4subscore'.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/R4SUB/r4subui
BugReports: https://github.com/R4SUB/r4subui/issues
